yzing Cook.ai, Pack&Profit, and other platforms) 4. Product Vision & Core Value Proposition 5. Technical Architecture & System Design 6. Feature Specifications with detailed breakdowns 7. Monetization Strategy & Revenue Models 8. Implementation Roadmap (Phases 1-4) 9. Go-to-Market Strategy 10. Success Metrics & KPIs Use professional styling with: - Clean, modern design with a tech/SaaS aesthetic - Color scheme: Navy blue (#1a365d), Teal accent (#0891b2), White/Gray backgrounds - Tables for feature comparisons, pricing, and roadmaps - Visual section dividers - Icons or emoji for key points - Callout boxes for important insights - Responsive design - Professional typography Include detailed tactical information such as: - Integration points (FB Ads API, Google Ads API, AI models) - Specific frameworks (Alex Hormozi's $100M Offers methodology) - Psychology-based copywriting principles - Audience insight extraction methods - Visual workflow builders - Asset generation capabilities - Real implementation steps Make it actionable and data-driven with specific recommendations, not generic advice. Perfect! I've created a comprehensive strategic business document for \"The Truth Engine\". Let me view it to confirm all sections are complete: Using Tool | Doc View Viewing document: 200,300 Using Tool | Doc View Viewing document: 300,465 Excellent! Now let me create a detailed tactical implementation table as a separate section. Let me enhance the document with more actionable details: Using Tool | Doc Edit --- a/document.html+++ b/document.html@@ -460,5 +460,361 @@       <li><strong>User Success:</strong> % of generated offers that launch live ads within 7 days.</li> <li><strong>Data Accuracy:</strong> Correlation between our \"Predicted Winning Angle\" and actual high CTRs.</li> </ul> + +    <!-- 11. Detailed Implementation SOP --> +    <h2>11. Detailed Implementation SOP (Step-by-Step)</h2> +    <p>This section provides click-by-click tactical instructions for building core components.</p> + +    <h3>SOP 1: Setting Up Meta Ad Library Data Pipeline</h3> +    <table> +      <thead> +        <tr> +          <th style=\"width: 5%\">#</th> +          <th style=\"width: 35%\">Action Step</th> +          <th style=\"width: 30%\">Expected Input</th> +          <th style=\"width: 30%\">Expected Output</th> +        </tr> +      </thead> +      <tbody> +        <tr> +          <td>1</td> +          <td>Register as Meta Developer</td> +          <td>Business email, Facebook account</td> +          <td>Developer App ID & Secret</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>2</td> +          <td>Request Ad Library API Access</td> +          <td>Business verification (EIN, website)</td> +          <td>Approved API credentials</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>3</td> +          <td>Install Python Library: <code>facebook-business</code></td> +          <td><code>pip install facebook-business</code></td> +          <td>Successfully imported SDK</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>4</td> +          <td>Write Search Query (Example: \"Solar sales training\")</td> +          <td>Keyword, country filter (US)</td> +          <td>JSON array of ads with creative URLs</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>5</td> +          <td>Filter by Ad Age (only ads running > 90 days)</td> +          <td>Start date from API response</td> +          <td>Filtered list of \"proven\" ads</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>6</td> +          <td>Store in PostgreSQL with fields: ad_id, image_url, body_text, cta_button, launch_date</td> +          <td>Normalized JSON</td> +          <td>Database record created</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>7</td> +          <td>Schedule cron job (daily refresh)</td> +          <td>Python scheduler (APScheduler)</td> +          <td>Automated daily updates</td> +        </tr> +      </tbody> +    </table> + +    <h3>SOP 2: Building the $100M Offer Framework Prompt Engine</h3> +    <table> +      <thead> +        <tr> +          <th style=\"width: 5%\">#</th> +          <th style=\"width: 35%\">Action Step</th> +          <th style=\"width: 30%\">Expected Input</th> +          <th style=\"width: 30%\">Expected Output</th> +        </tr> +      </thead> +      <tbody> +        <tr> +          <td>1</td> +          <td>Study Alex Hormozi's Value Equation: Dream Outcome × Likelihood / (Time Delay × Effort & Sacrifice)</td> +          <td>Book notes, YouTube transcripts</td> +          <td>Structured understanding of 4 variables</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>2</td> +          <td>Create JSON template for each variable</td> +          <td>{ \"dream_outcome\": \"\", \"likelihood\": \"\", \"time_delay\": \"\", \"effort\": \"\" }</td> +          <td>Validated JSON schema</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>3</td> +          <td>Write GPT-4 system prompt: \"You are an expert in Alex Hormozi's framework. Analyze the following ad copy and extract the implied offer...\"</td> +          <td>Ad copy text from database</td> +          <td>Structured offer breakdown</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>4</td> +          <td>Test on 20 known winning offers manually</td> +          <td>Sample ads from ClickFunnels, Russell Brunson</td> +          <td>85%+ accuracy in identifying value elements</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>5</td> +          <td>Iterate prompt with \"few-shot examples\"</td> +          <td>3-5 labeled examples in prompt</td> +          <td>Improved consistency in output format</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>6</td> +          <td>Build API endpoint: /api/analyze-offer (POST)</td> +          <td>{\"ad_text\": \"...\"}</td> +          <td>{\"dream_outcome\": \"...\", \"likelihood\": \"...\", ...}</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>7</td> +          <td>Connect to frontend dashboard component</td> +          <td>User clicks \"Analyze Competitor\"</td> +          <td>Visual card showing offer breakdown</td> +        </tr> +      </tbody> +    </table> + +    <h3>SOP 3: Creating Visual Workflow Builder for Funnels</h3> +    <table> +      <thead> +        <tr> +          <th style=\"width: 5%\">#</th> +          <th style=\"width: 35%\">Action Step</th> +          <th style=\"width: 30%\">Expected Input</th> +          <th style=\"width: 30%\">Expected Output</th> +        </tr> +      </thead> +      <tbody> +        <tr> +          <td>1</td> +          <td>Choose React Flow library for drag-and-drop nodes</td> +          <td><code>npm install reactflow</code></td> +          <td>Installed library in Next.js project</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>2</td> +          <td>Define node types: Ad → Landing Page → Checkout → Thank You</td> +          <td>Custom node components</td> +          <td>4 reusable node types</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>3</td> +          <td>Connect nodes with edges (conversion flow)</td> +          <td>User drags from output → input</td> +          <td>Visual flow representation</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>4</td> +          <td>Add \"Smart Suggestions\" based on offer type</td> +          <td>Offer type: \"Webinar\" or \"Low Ticket\"</td> +          <td>Pre-configured template auto-loads</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>5</td> +          <td>Generate copy for each node using AI</td> +          <td>Node position + offer context</td> +          <td>\"Ad Headline\", \"LP Hero Section\" auto-populated</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>6</td> +          <td>Export to JSON for integration with GHL</td> +          <td>Click \"Export to GoHighLevel\"</td> +          <td>API call creates funnel pages in GHL account</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>7</td> +          <td>Test integration with GHL sandbox account</td> +          <td>API credentials from GHL</td> +          <td>Funnel appears in GHL dashboard</td> +        </tr> +      </tbody> +    </table> + +    <!-- 12. Psychology & Copywriting Principles Library --> +    <h2>12. Psychology & Copywriting Principles Engine</h2> +    <p>The Truth Engine incorporates deep psychological triggers beyond basic AI copywriting.</p> + +    <h3>Core Psychology Frameworks Embedded</h3> +    <table> +      <thead> +        <tr> +          <th>Principle</th> +          <th>Source</th> +          <th>Application in Truth Engine</th> +          <th>Example Output</th> +        </tr> +      </thead> +      <tbody> +        <tr> +          <td><strong>Scarcity</strong></td> +          <td>Cialdini - Influence</td> +          <td>Auto-adds time-bound urgency to offers</td> +          <td>\"Only 47 spots remain before doors close\"</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td><strong>Social Proof</strong></td> +          <td>Cialdini - Influence</td> +          <td>Extracts testimonial patterns from competitor ads</td> +          <td>\"Join 12,438 successful students\"</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td><strong>The Gap Theory</strong></td> +          <td>Dan Kennedy</td> +          <td>Identifies the \"current state vs. desired state\"</td> +          <td>\"From $0 to $10K/mo in 90 days\"</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td><strong>Risk Reversal</strong></td> +          <td>Hormozi - $100M Offers</td> +          <td>Generates strong guarantees</td> +          <td>\"We'll refund you + pay you $100 if you don't see results\"</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td><strong>PAS Framework</strong></td> +          <td>Problem-Agitate-Solve</td> +          <td>Structures long-form sales copy</td> +          <td>Problem hook → pain amplification → solution reveal</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td><strong>Value Stacking</strong></td> +          <td>Russell Brunson</td> +          <td>Lists bonuses to increase perceived value</td> +          <td>\"Bonus #1 ($497 value), Bonus #2 ($297 value)...\"</td> +        </tr> +      </tbody> +    </table> + +    <div class=\"callout\"> +      <strong>Implementation Note:</strong> +      Each principle is coded as a separate \"prompt modifier\" in our AI engine. When generating copy, the system +      selectively activates 3-5 principles based on the offer type and audience pain points discovered in research. +    </div> + +    <!-- 13. Data Sources & Research Integration --> +    <h2>13. Comprehensive Data Sources Matrix</h2> +    <table> +      <thead> +        <tr> +          <th>Data Source</th> +          <th>Integration Method</th> +          <th>Data Points Extracted</th> +          <th>Cost/Limitations</th> +        </tr> +      </thead> +      <tbody> +        <tr> +          <td><strong>Meta Ad Library API</strong></td> +          <td>Official API (Free)</td> +          <td>Ad creative, body text, CTA, launch date, impressions range</td> +          <td>Rate limited (200 calls/hour)</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td><strong>Google Ads Transparency Center</strong></td> +          <td>Web scraping (SerpApi)</td> +          <td>Advertiser name, ad copy, keywords, landing pages</td> +          <td>$50/mo for 5,000 searches</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td><strong>SpyFu API</strong></td> +          <td>Paid API</td> +          <td>Estimated ad spend, organic keywords, competitor domain rankings</td> +          <td>Starting at $39/mo</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td><strong>SEMRush API</strong></td> +          <td>Paid API</td> +          <td>Backlinks, traffic estimates, keyword difficulty</td> +          <td>Starting at $129/mo</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td><strong>Reddit API</strong></td> +          <td>Official API (PRAW - Python)</td> +          <td>User complaints, feature requests, pain points</td> +          <td>Free (rate limited)</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td><strong>YouTube Transcript API</strong></td> +          <td>youtube-transcript-api (Python)</td> +          <td>Video hooks, VSL scripts, teaching methodologies</td> +          <td>Free (public videos only)</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td><strong>GoHighLevel API</strong></td> +          <td>Official API</td> +          <td>Export funnels, contacts, automations directly</td> +          <td>Free (requires GHL account)</td> +        </tr> +      </tbody> +    </table> + +    <!-- 14. Competitive Differentiators --> +    <h2>14. Why Truth Engine Wins (Competitive Moats)</h2> +    <div class=\"framework-box\"> +      <div class=\"framework-step\"> +        <h4>🎯 Data Moat</h4> +        <p>Our database of 500K+ analyzed winning ads becomes smarter over time. Competitors start from scratch.</p> +      </div> +      <div class=\"framework-step\"> +        <h4>🧠 Framework Moat</h4> +        <p>Exclusive implementation of Hormozi's $100M methodology. Not just copywriting, but strategic offer design.</p> +      </div> +      <div class=\"framework-step\"> +        <h4>⚡ Speed Moat</h4> +        <p>From idea to validated offer in 20 minutes vs. 20 hours of manual research.</p> +      </div> +    </div> + +    <!-- 15. Risk Mitigation --> +    <h2>15. Risk Analysis & Mitigation Strategy</h2> +    <table> +      <thead> +        <tr> +          <th>Risk</th> +          <th>Probability</th> +          <th>Impact</th> +          <th>Mitigation Strategy</th> +        </tr> +      </thead> +      <tbody> +        <tr> +          <td>API Rate Limits (Meta/Google)</td> +          <td><span class=\"status-tag status-high\">High</span></td> +          <td><span class=\"status-tag status-med\">Medium</span></td> +          <td>Implement caching, rotating proxy IPs, batch processing during off-peak hours</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>AI Hallucination (Incorrect Insights)</td> +          <td><span class=\"status-tag status-med\">Medium</span></td> +          <td><span class=\"status-tag status-high\">High</span></td> +          <td>Human-in-the-loop review for first 100 users; confidence scores on all outputs</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>Competitor Cloning Feature Set</td> +          <td><span class=\"status-tag status-med\">Medium</span></td> +          <td><span class=\"status-tag status-med\">Medium</span></td> +          <td>Build proprietary dataset; focus on user experience superiority</td> +        </tr> +        <tr> +          <td>User Misuse (Spammy Offers)</td> +          <td><span class=\"status-tag status-low\">Low</span></td> +          <td><span class=\"status-tag status-med\">Medium</span></td> +          <td>Usage policy; ethical guidelines baked into AI prompts</td> +        </tr> +      </tbody> +    </table> + +    <!-- Final CTA --> +    <div class=\"callout\" style=\"margin-top: 50px; border-color: var(--primary); background-color: #f0f9ff;\"> +      <strong>Next Steps:</strong> +      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\"> +        1. <strong>Technical Validation:</strong> Build Phase 1 (Data Crawler) MVP in 30 days<br /> +        2. <strong>Market Validation:</strong> Pre-sell 50 \"Founder\" accounts at $197 lifetime<br /> +        3. <strong>Funding Strategy:</strong> Bootstrap to $10K MRR, then consider $250K seed round for team expansion +      </p> +    </div> + </body> </html> Perfect! Now let me create visual flowcharts and diagrams to illustrate the system. Let me generate a comprehensive system architecture diagram: Using Tool | Think The user wants interactive infographics, images, flowcharts and charts to describe every process we design. I should use the programmatic_visualization tool to create: 1. System Architecture Diagram - showing how all components connect 2. User Journey Flowchart - from research to launch 3. Data Flow Diagram - how data moves through the system 4. Monetization Model Comparison Chart 5. Market Positioning Matrix These will make the document much more actionable and visual. Let me create the