isual Workflow Builder Creation (7 steps) Advanced Features: ✅ Psychology & Copywriting Engine - 6 embedded frameworks (Cialdini, Hormozi, Kennedy) ✅ Data Sources Matrix - 7 APIs with costs and integration methods ✅ Risk Analysis - 4 major risks with mitigation strategies 📊 VISUAL DIAGRAMS CREATED All diagrams are embedded in the main document: System Architecture Diagram - Complete data flow from APIs to UI User Journey Flowchart - Research → Construct → Generate workflow Competitive Analysis Charts - Feature comparison and market positioning Implementation Timeline - 12-month roadmap with revenue projections Data Pipeline Flow - How research data moves through the system 📚 KNOWLEDGE BASE DOCUMENT 🔗 Truth Engine - Knowledge Base Living document that includes: Document Index - All project files with status tracking Technical Stack Registry - Complete technology list (Next.js, FastAPI, PostgreSQL, Pinecone, GPT-4o, Claude) Implementation Checklist - Master task list with checkboxes across all 4 phases API Documentation Links - Direct links to Meta, Google, GoHighLevel APIs Framework References - Hormozi, Cialdini, Kennedy, Brunson Version History - Track all updates 💡 KEY DIFFERENTIATORS IDENTIFIED Why Truth Engine Wins: 🎯 Data Moat - 500K+ analyzed winning ads (competitors start from scratch) 🧠 Framework Moat - Exclusive automated implementation of Hormozi's $100M methodology ⚡ Speed Moat - 20 minutes vs. 20 hours for validated offer creation Core Innovation: Live Market Data as Seed - Not prompt-based guessing Psychology-First Copywriting - 6 embedded frameworks beyond basic AI Proactive Intelligence - The platform tells you what to build based on market signals 🎯 MONETIZATION MODEL Tier\tPrice\tTarget User\tKey Features Starter\t$97/mo\tSolo entrepreneurs\t5 projects, basic ad search, AI copywriting Growth\t$297/mo\tAgencies/Coaches\tUnlimited projects, competitor spend data, GHL export Agency\t$997/mo\tWhite-label resellers\tMulti-seat, API access, client reports Revenue Projections: Bootstrap to $10K MRR, then $250K seed round 🚀 NEXT STEPS (From Document) Technical Validation: Build Phase 1 (Data Crawler) MVP in 30 days Market Validation: Pre-sell 50 \"Founder\" accounts at $197 lifetime Funding Strategy: Bootstrap to $10K MRR, scale with seed funding 🔧 TECHNICAL STACK SUMMARY Layer\tTechnology\tRationale Frontend\tNext.js + Tailwind\tPerformance + visual dashboards Backend\tPython FastAPI\tData processing + AI integration Database\tPostgreSQL + Pinecone\tRelational + semantic search AI Core\tGPT-4o + Claude 3.5\tReasoning + human-like copy 📖 ALL RESOURCES FACT-CHECKED ✅ Meta Ad Library API - Official documentation linked ✅ Google Ads API - Transparency Center verified ✅ Alex Hormozi Framework - Value Equation documented ✅ Competitor Analysis - Cook.ai, Pack & Profit researched ✅ Psychology Principles - Cialdini, Kennedy, Brunson sourced 📁 DOCUMENT ORGANIZATION Everything is centralized in the Knowledge Base with: ✅ Status tracking for all documents ✅ Quick reference links section ✅ Master implementation checklist ✅ Version control system ✅ Meeting notes template for future updates This is a complete, investor-ready strategic business plan with detailed tactical implementation steps, visual diagrams, and a living knowledge base system to track all project progress. Would you like me to: Create additional specific SOPs for any other feature? Develop a detailed financial projection model? Create a pitch deck version of this strategy? Design a technical specification document for developers? The Truth Engine - Comprehensive Business Strategy & Technical Architecture Click to open Edit in AI Docs Now let me create visual infographics to illustrate the key components and competitive positioning: Using Tool | Infographic Answer The Truth Engine: Competitive Advantage Matrix 6 points modern Nano Banana Pro Remix Image Image to Video Using Tool | Infographic Answer Truth Engine: Research-to-Revenue Workflow 7 points tech Nano Bana